BT 1 0 0 1 0 66 Tm /F1 11 Tf 15.4 TL (InfraSight is a full-stack ICT infrastructure monitoring and predictive maintenance system) Tj T* (developed for Great Zimbabwe University. It enables ICT administrators to monitor institutional) Tj T* (network and computing infrastructure, detect abnormal device behaviour, predict possible device) Tj T* (faults before they cause outages, generate and manage alerts, validate fault scenarios, and) Tj T* (present measurable evaluation evidence.) Tj T* ET
Q
Q
q
1 0 0 1 62.69291 609.9969 cm
q
0 0 0 rg
BT 1 0 0 1 0 35.2 Tm /F1 11 Tf 15.4 TL (The system uses a Random Forest machine learning model trained on telemetry data from five) Tj T* (device categories including servers, switches, routers, access points, and workstations. It) Tj T* (classifies each device as normal or fault-prone based on eight monitored metrics.) Tj T* ET
