BT 1 0 0 1 0 127.6 Tm /F1 11 Tf 15.4 TL (InfraSight is a complete, verified, and deployable ICT infrastructure monitoring and predictive) Tj T* (maintenance system designed for Great Zimbabwe University. The system demonstrates how) Tj T* (machine learning can improve fault detection, reduce response time, and support proactive) Tj T* (maintenance decisions. Key achievements include a Random Forest prediction engine using) Tj T* (eight telemetry variables, 81 percent reduction in fault detection time, live Firebase cloud) Tj T* (integration, complete alert management, four validated scenarios, production-ready Vercel and) Tj T* (Render configuration, examiner-ready Demo Mode, and PDF evidence export. InfraSight) Tj T* (provides a strong academic contribution by combining real-time monitoring, machine learning,) Tj T* (cloud services, and evidence-based evaluation into one demonstrable dissertation prototype.) Tj T* ET
